# ORIS Final Acceptance API

A small in-memory task-board API built with FastAPI.

## Setup

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
. .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## Test

```bash
python3 -m py_compile app/main.py
pytest -q
```

## API

- `GET /health`
- `GET /capabilities`
- `GET /tasks`
- `POST /tasks`
- `GET /tasks/{task_id}`
- `PATCH /tasks/{task_id}`
